---

<ServicePageDetailed
  title="Mercury-Free Dentistry"
  subtitle="Safe Amalgam Removal & Biocompatible Restorations"
  description="Safe mercury amalgam removal and biocompatible dentistry in Dallas"
  metaDescription="Safe mercury amalgam removal and biocompatible dentistry in Dallas. We use the SMART protocol for mercury-free fillings and restorations."
  backgroundImage="/images/services/abstract-white-texture.jpg"
>
  <!-- Main Content - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12">

          <!-- Main Content Column -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-2">
            <!-- Introduction -->
            <BlurFade delay={100}>
              <div class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary mb-6">
                  Your Health Deserves Mercury-Free Solutions
                </h2>
                <p class="text-body-large text-gray-dark mb-6">
                  At Central Dentist, we've been mercury-free for over 30 years. We believe that your dental
                  care shouldn't compromise your overall health. That's why we exclusively use biocompatible
                  materials and follow the strictest safety protocols for amalgam removal.
                </p>
                <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">
                  Mercury is continuously emitted from amalgam fillings and absorbed by your body, particularly
                  affecting the brain, kidneys, liver, lungs, and gastrointestinal tract. We're committed to
                  providing safer alternatives that protect both your oral and systemic health.
                </p>
              </div>
            </BlurFade>

            <!-- SMART Protocol Section -->
            <BlurFade delay={200}>
              <div class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary mb-6">
                  Safe Mercury Amalgam Removal Technique (SMART)
                </h2>
                <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium mb-8">
                  We follow the SMART protocol developed by the International Academy of Oral Medicine and
                  Toxicology (IAOMT) to ensure your safety during amalgam removal:
                </p>

                <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
                  {protocolSteps.map((section) => (
                    <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
                      <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-secondary mb-4">{section.title}</h3>
                      <ul class="space-y-3">
                        {section.items.map((item) => (
                          <li class="flex items-start">
                            <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                            <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">{item}</span>
                          </li>
                        ))}
                      </ul>
                    </Card>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            </BlurFade>
          </div>

          <!-- Sidebar Column -->
          <div class="lg:col-span-1">
            <div class="sticky top-24 space-y-6">
              <!-- Quick Facts Card -->
              <Card variant="bordered" class="p-6">
                <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-primary mb-4">
                  Mercury-Free Since 1990
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #a6b443;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-body-small text-gray-medium">SMART certified practitioners</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #a6b443;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-body-small text-gray-medium">IAOMT member practice</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #a6b443;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-body-small text-gray-medium">EPA-compliant disposal</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" style="color: #a6b443;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-body-small text-gray-medium">Air filtration systems</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </Card>

              <!-- CTA Card -->
              <div class="rounded-xl p-6 text-white" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0099ba, #006786);">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-normal mb-3 text-white" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
                  Ready to Go Mercury-Free?
                </h3>
                <p class="text-white/90 mb-4 text-sm">
                  Schedule your consultation to discuss safe amalgam removal.
                </p>
                <a
                  href="/contact"
                  class="block w-full text-center px-6 py-2 bg-white rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg"
                  style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #0099ba;"
                >
                  Book Consultation
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Health Concerns Section - Gray Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              Why Remove Mercury Amalgam?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              Research has linked mercury exposure from dental amalgams to numerous health conditions
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
          {healthConcerns.map((concern, index) => (
            <BlurFade delay={200 + index * 100}>
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center" style={`background-color: ${concern.color};`}>
                  <span class="text-3xl">{concern.icon}</span>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-primary mb-3">{concern.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">
                  {concern.description}
                </p>
              </div>
            </BlurFade>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Biocompatible Alternatives - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              Biocompatible Alternatives
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              Superior alternatives to mercury amalgam that are both safer and more aesthetic
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <BlurFade delay={200}>
            <Card variant="bordered" class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-secondary mb-4">
                Composite Resin Restorations
              </h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium mb-6">
                BPA-free, tooth-colored materials that bond directly to your tooth structure,
                preserving more of your natural tooth while providing excellent durability and aesthetics.
              </p>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                {['Natural appearance', 'Minimal tooth removal', 'No mercury or metals', 'Repairable if damaged'].map((benefit) => (
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-3" style="color: #a6b443;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">{benefit}</span>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </Card>
          </BlurFade>

          <BlurFade delay={300}>
            <Card variant="bordered" class="p-8">
              <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-secondary mb-4">
                Ceramic Restorations
              </h3>
              <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium mb-6">
                For larger restorations, we offer ceramic inlays, onlays, and crowns that provide
                superior strength and longevity without any metals or toxins.
              </p>
              <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                {['Exceptional durability', '100% biocompatible', 'Stain resistant', 'Natural translucency'].map((benefit) => (
                  <div class="flex items-center">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-3" style="color: #a6b443;" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                    </svg>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">{benefit}</span>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </Card>
          </BlurFade>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Detoxification Support - Gray Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              Detoxification Support
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              We support your body's natural detoxification processes before and after amalgam removal
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <BlurFade delay={200}>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-secondary mb-4">
                  Pre-Removal Preparation
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">Nutritional assessment and optimization</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">Supplementation protocols to support detox pathways</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">Immune system strengthening</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>

              <div>
                <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-secondary mb-4">
                  Post-Removal Support
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-3">
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">Activated charcoal and chlorella protocols</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">Vitamin C and glutathione support</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #0099ba;">‚Ä¢</span>
                    <span class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">Monitoring and follow-up care</span>
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              Frequently Asked Questions
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              Learn more about mercury-free dentistry
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <BlurFade delay={200}>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            {faqs.map((faq) => (
              <details class="group bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer p-6 hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
                  <span class="text-body-regular font-semibold text-gray-dark pr-4">{faq.question}</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 flex-shrink-0 transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" style="color: #0099ba;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
                  </svg>
                </summary>
                <div class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0">
                  <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">{faq.answer}</p>
                </div>
              </details>
            ))}
          </div>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section - Blue Gradient Background -->
  <section slot="cta" class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0099ba, #006786);">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal text-white mb-4"
              style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
            Ready for Mercury-Free Dentistry?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/90 mb-8" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">
            Take the first step toward safer, biocompatible dental care. Schedule your consultation
            to discuss mercury amalgam removal and healthier alternatives.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#a6b443] to-[#c7cd85] text-white rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:from-[#8fa339] hover:to-[#a6b443] hover:shadow-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center"
              style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;"
            >
              Schedule Consultation
            </a>
            <a
              href="tel:214-368-0900"
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-white border-2 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center"
              style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #0099ba; border-color: white;"
              onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#006786'; this.style.color='white'; this.style.borderColor='#006786';"
              onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='white'; this.style.color='#0099ba'; this.style.borderColor='white';"
            >
              <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              Call (214) 368-0900
            </a>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServicePageDetailed>